                <fr:title text="The indicator function of a subset">The indicator function of a subset</fr:title>
                <fr:taxon>Definition</fr:taxon>
              </fr:frontmatter>
              <fr:mainmatter>
                <html:p>The <html:em><html:strong>indicator function</html:strong></html:em> or <html:em><html:strong>characteristic function</html:strong></html:em> of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[S\subseteq  A]]></fr:tex> is defined to be the <fr:link href="/jms-00LO/" title="Predicate" uri="https://www.jonmsterling.com/jms-00LO/" display-uri="jms-00LO" type="local">predicate</fr:link> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\chi _S\colon  A\to  {\mathopen {}\left  [2\right  ]\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex> defined piecewise below:</html:p>
                <fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[
 \chi _S{\mathopen {}\left (a\right )\mathclose {}} = \begin {cases}
  1 & \text {if } a \in  S\\
  0 & \text {if } a \not \in  S
 \end {cases}
]]></fr:tex>
              </fr:mainmatter>
